<li id="cite_note-Joint_Custody_Best_for_Most_Children-22"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Joint_Custody_Best_for_Most_Children_22-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Joint_Custody_Best_for_Most_Children_22-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Joint_Custody_Best_for_Most_Children_22-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Joint_Custody_Best_for_Most_Children_22-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation web">Lerche Davis, Jeanie. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.webmd.com/baby/news/20020325/joint-custody-best-for-most-children">"Joint Custody Best for Most Children"</a>. <i>WebMD Health News</i>. WebMD, Inc.<span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.webmd.com/baby/news/20020325/joint-custody-best-for-most-children">http://www.webmd.com/baby/news/20020325/joint-custody-best-for-most-children</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 27 September 2011</span>.</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-Child_adjustment_in_joint-custody_versus_sole-custody_arrangements:_A_meta-analytic_review-23"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Child_adjustment_in_joint-custody_versus_sole-custody_arrangements:_A_meta-analytic_review_23-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Child_adjustment_in_joint-custody_versus_sole-custody_arrangements:_A_meta-analytic_review_23-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text">Bauserman, R. (2002). Child adjustment in joint-custody versus sole-custody arrangements: A meta-analytic review. Journal of Family Psychology, 16(1), 91-102. <a href="Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1037/0893-3200.16.1.91">10.1037/0893-3200.16.1.91</a></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-Joint_Custody_Best_for_Kids_After_Divorce-24"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Joint_Custody_Best_for_Kids_After_Divorce_24-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Joint_Custody_Best_for_Kids_After_Divorce_24-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Joint_Custody_Best_for_Kids_After_Divorce_24-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Joint_Custody_Best_for_Kids_After_Divorce_24-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Joint_Custody_Best_for_Kids_After_Divorce_24-4"><sup><i><b>e</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Joint_Custody_Best_for_Kids_After_Divorce_24-5"><sup><i><b>f</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Joint_Custody_Best_for_Kids_After_Divorce_24-6"><sup><i><b>g</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation news">Peterson, Karen S. (24 March 2002). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.usatoday.com/news/health/child/2002-03-25-joint-custody.htm">"Joint Custody Best for Kids After Divorce"</a>. <i>USATODAY.com</i><span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.usatoday.com/news/health/child/2002-03-25-joint-custody.htm">http://www.usatoday.com/news/health/child/2002-03-25-joint-custody.htm</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 27 September 2011</span>.</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-Child_Adjustment_In_Joint-Custody_Versus_Sole-Custody_Arrangements-25"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Child_Adjustment_In_Joint-Custody_Versus_Sole-Custody_Arrangements_25-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Child_Adjustment_In_Joint-Custody_Versus_Sole-Custody_Arrangements_25-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation Journal">Bauserman, R (2002). "Child adjustment in joint-custody versus sole-custody arrangements: A meta-analytic review". <i>Journal of Family Psychology</i> <b>16</b> (1): 91–102. <a href="Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1037/0893-3200.16.1.91">10.1037/0893-3200.16.1.91</a>.</span></span></li>
